>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Schapiro-9\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Schapiro_9-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\">Schapiro, 100</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-10\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-10\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nga.gov.au/exhibition/masterpiecesfromparis/Default.cfm?IRN=191186&amp;BioArtistIRN=21796&amp;MnuID=SRCH&amp;ArtistIRN=21796&amp;ViewID=2\">\"Gustave Geffroy 1895-96\"</a>. National Gallery of Australia. 2009<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">2011-04-30</span></span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=unknown&amp;rft.btitle=Gustave+Geffroy+1895-96&amp;rft.pub=National+Gallery+of+Australia&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fnga.gov.au%2Fexhibition%2Fmasterpiecesfromparis%2FDefault.cfm%3FIRN%3D191186%26BioArtistIRN%3D21796%26MnuID%3DSRCH%26ArtistIRN%3D21796%26ViewID%3D2&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3APortrait+of+Gustave+Geffroy\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Sources\">Sources</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Portrait_of_Gustave_Geffroy&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Sources\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li>Howard, Michael. <i>C\u00e9zanne</i>. New York: Gallery Books, 1990. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/0-8317-2827-2\" title=\"Special:BookSources/0-8317-2827-2\">0-8317-2827-2</a></li>\n<li>Murphy, Richard W. <i>The World of C\u00e9zanne</i>. New York: Time-Life Books, 196